## Technical Implementation

The platform uses consistent routing patterns across collections:
- Analytics: `/analytics/{slug}`
- Experiment: `/feature-experiment/{slug}`
- APIs: `/apis/{category}/{slug}`
- SDKs: `/sdks/{category}/{slug}`
- Data: `/data/{category}/{slug}`

Collections support preview functionality, URL-based routing, and hierarchical content organization with navigation injection for consistent user experience across the documentation ecosystem.

The platform maintains separate content structures for different locales (English and Japanese) with propagation controls and site-specific configurations.